Package: finViz
Type: Package
Title: Create Financial Summaries and Visuals
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "James", "Del Mutolo",
      email = "delmutoloj@usf.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package provides functions for analyzing financial data and
    generating visualizations, with a focus on Sankey diagrams. It includes
    tools for calculating key financial metrics, tracking income and expenses,
    and creating intuitive flow-based visualizations to assist with budgeting
    and financial planning.
